
Ranger Help for: stalk
======================

SYNTAX:      stalk <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   11
BASE SP:     20 initially, 10 sp per move
SKILL TYPE:  tracking

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to trail close behind or follow a query through
any area the query can go. Several things can cause a Ranger to lose his
or her query, such as the query is wiser than the Ranger, or just by
chance, or if the Ranger runs out of stamina points. Rangers can only trail
less wise Rangers than themselves.

